 and negative values. I plan to use these validation rules on `onChange` to give instant feedback. I'll now build the page layout!\n\n\n**Modeling Financial Projections**\n\nI'm now integrating year-over-year financial projections. I will visualize Year 1's savings against investment, followed by Year 2 at full run-rate, and finally, Year 3's anticipated savings. This multi-year presentation elevates the tool's perceived strategic value. I plan to present these projections clearly and concisely.\n\nI'm now working to create the SVG agent flow diagram within the page. I'll need to research how to generate an inline SVG with the correct styling and interactivity within the page, based on the user's inputs. I will draft out the file structure, and define key imports before starting on the SVG code. I'm focusing on crafting a very premium look and feel.\n\n\n**Refining Styling Implementation**\n\nI'm now diving into the styling details for the executive ROI calculator's user interface. I want to ensure every element, especially the input fields and segmented controls, feels premium and modern. I'm focusing on the white/5 border with a border-[#009DFF] focus state for inputs. I'm planning muted help texts with subtle glows. I'm also preparing beautiful segmented controls, with the active button's specific background, border, and text colors. I've reconfirmed that I only need to modify `/app/build/roi/page.tsx` for this task.\n\n\n**Calculating Projection Outputs**\n\nI'm now calculating financial projections, and I've modeled annual savings using parsed inputs and defined variables. The `baseCapCost` scales by company size. I've also implemented an effort multiplier with the segmented control to estimate savings. Now I'm working on the investment calculations to present the ROI and payback projections.\n\n\n**Visualizing Agent Workflows**\n\nI'm now implementing the interactive agent workflow map in the preview, dynamically rendering different flows based on the chosen functional domain. I'm planning SVG diagrams for \"Customer Operations,\" \"Finance & Accounting,\" and \"Legal & Compliance,\" with tailored steps and a clean visual style for each. I'm focusing on making them interactive.\n\n\n**Designing Agent Workflow Flows**\n\nI'm now detailing the functional domain agent workflows within the interactive map. For \"Human Resources,\" I'll render \"Employee Inquiry -> Policy Retriever -> HR Agent -> Sovereign Reply -> VPC Sandbox\". \"IT & Security\" will show \"System Log -> Event Classifier -> Enclave Mitigator -> Secure Response -> Watched Action.\" For \"Operations / Supply Chain,\" I'll render \"Supplier Query -> Line-item Matcher -> VPC Procurement Agent -> Sovereign Proposal -> Push\".\n\n\\n\\n\n\nThese agent workflow visualizations will respond to left-side selection changes. They really add premium design elements. I will be incorporating all of these key elements: agent workflow map, Bento grid, interactive selector, animated background, and CTA sections. I'll focus on replacing the content of `/app/build/roi/page.tsx` with a beautifully designed, interactive page component.\n\n\n**Finalizing Premium Implementation**\n\nI'm now writing the complete code for `/app/build/roi/page.tsx`, focusing on a premium design. I'm double-checking requirements and ensuring validation, edge cases, and disclaimer adherence. All necessary input fields and error handling are included for a seamless user experience. I'm focusing on illustrative, model outputs.\n\n\n**Finalizing Interface Details**\n\nI'm now integrating all elements of `/app/build/roi/page.tsx`, and I'm polishing the interactive calculator with the agent flow and premium UI. I'm leveraging the constants to ensure consistency. The focus is on a seamless build with zero errors. All edge cases, including valid inputs, are considered. I have the calculator and interactive preview perfectly aligned.\n\n\n"}}
{"ts":"2026-06-26T18:58:51.217Z","type":"agent_event","event":{"type":"content_start","contentType":"tool","toolName":"editor","toolCallId":"kig84n4i","input":{"path":"/Users/ayushbansal/Documents/GitHub/hirezapp_landing_page/app/build/roi/page.tsx","old_text":null,"new_text":"\"use client\";\n\nimport React, { useState, useMemo } from \"react\";\nimport { motion, AnimatePresence } from \"motion/react\";\nimport { ToolPageShell, ToolPreviewNotice, ToolCTA } from \"@/components/build/components\";\nimport { SHARED_INDUSTRIES, SHARED_COMPANY_SIZES } from \"@/lib/shared-constants\";\n\n// Define the form inputs interface\ninterface ROICalculatorState {\n  industry: string;\n  companySize: string;\n  functionalDomain: string;\n  annualCostBaseline: string;\n  processVolume: string;\n  avgHandlingTime: string; // Optional\n  automationTarget: number;\n  currentManualEffort: \"Low\" | \"Medium\" | \"High\";\n  expectedProductivityImprovement: number;\n  implementationHorizon: \"3 Months\" | \"6 Months\" | \"12 Months\";\n}\n\n// Validation errors state\ninterface ValidationErrors {\n  annualCostBaseline?: string;\n  processVolume?: string;\n  avgHandlingTime?: string;\n}\n\nexport default function ROICalculatorPage() {\n  // 1. Core State\n  const [formData, setFormData] = useState<ROICalculatorState>({\n    industry: \"Financial Services\",\n    companySize: \"1000-10000\",\n    functionalDomain: \"Finance & Accounting\",\n    annualCostBaseline: \"450000\",\n    processVolume: \"125000\",\n    avgHandlingTime: \"15\", // optional, in minutes\n    automationTarget: 70, // percentage slider\n    currentManualEffort: \"High\",\n    expectedProductivityImprovement: 45, // percentage slider\n    implementationHorizon: \"6 Months\",\n  });\n\n  const [errors, setErrors] = useState<ValidationErrors>({});\n  const [showReportModal, setShowReportModal] = useState(false);\n  const [isSimulating, setIsSimulating] = useState(false);\n\n  // 2. Functional Domains for Selection\n  const functionalDomains = [\n    { id: \"Finance & Accounting\", label: \"Finance & Accounting\", icon: \"📊\" },\n    { id: \"Customer Operations\", label: \"Customer Operations\", icon: \"🤝\" },\n    { id: \"Legal & Compliance\", label: \"Legal & Compliance\", icon: \"🛡️\" },\n    { id: \"Human Resources\", label: \"Human Resources\", icon: \"👥\" },\n    { id: \"IT & Security Ops\", label: \"IT & Security Ops\", icon: \"⚡\" },\n    { id: \"Supply Chain & Ops\", label: \"Supply Chain & Ops\", icon: \"🌐\" },\n  ];\n\n  // 3. Validation Helpers\n  const handleInputChange = (field: keyof ROICalculatorState, value: string | number) => {\n    // Basic state update\n    setFormData((prev) => ({\n      ...prev,\n      [field]: value,\n    }));\n\n    // Trigger field-specific validations\n    const strVal = String(value).trim();\n    const newErrors = { ...errors };\n\n    if (field === \"annualCostBaseline\") {\n      if (strVal === \"\") {\n        newErrors.annualCostBaseline = \"Annual baseline cost is required.\";\n      } else {\n        const parsed = parseFloat(strVal);\n        if (isNaN(parsed)) {\n          newErrors.annualCostBaseline = \"Please enter a valid number.\";\n        } else if (parsed < 0) {\n          newErrors.annualCostBaseline = \"Baseline cost cannot be negative.\";\n        } else {\n          delete newErrors.annualCostBaseline;\n        }\n      }\n    }\n\n    if (field === \"processVolume\") {\n      if (strVal === \"\") {\n        newErrors.processVolume = \"Process volume is required.\";\n      } else {\n        const parsed = parseFloat(strVal);\n        if (isNaN(parsed)) {\n          newErrors.processVolume = \"Please enter a valid number.\";\n        } else if (parsed < 0) {\n          newErrors.processVolume = \"Process volume cannot be negative.\";\n        } else {\n          delete newErrors.processVolume;\n        }\n      }\n    }\n\n    if (field === \"avgHandlingTime\") {\n      if (strVal === \"\") {\n        delete newErrors.avgHandlingTime; // Optional field\n      } else {\n        const parsed = parseFloat(strVal);\n        if (isNaN(parsed)) {\n          newErrors.avgHandlingTime = \"Please enter a valid number.\";\n        } else if (parsed < 0) {\n          newErrors.avgHandlingTime = \"Handling time cannot be negative.\";\n        } else {\n          delete newErrors.avgHandlingTime;\n        }\n      }\n    }\n\n    setErrors(newErrors);\n  };\n\n  // 4. Model Calculations\n  const calculatedModel = useMemo(() => {\n    // Check if any error exists\n    const hasErrors = Object.keys(errors).length > 0;\n    if (hasErrors) return null;\n\n    const parsedCost = parseFloat(formData.annualCostBaseline) || 0;\n    const parsedVolume = parseFloat(formData.processVolume) || 0;\n    const parsedHandlingTime = formData.avgHandlingTime ? parseFloat(formData.avgHandlingTime) : 0;\n\n    // Effort Multiplier (High = 1.25, Medium = 1.0, Low = 0.75)\n    const effortMultiplier =\n      formData.currentManualEffort === \"High\"\n        ? 1.25\n        : formData.currentManualEffort === \"Medium\"\n        ? 1.0\n        : 0.75;\n\n    const targetRate = formData.automationTarget / 100;\n    const improvementRate = formData.expectedProductivityImprovement / 100;\n\n    // Projected Annual Gross Savings Model\n    // Formulated: Baseline * Automation Target % * Productivity Improvement % * Effort Factor\n    const rawSavings = parsedCost * targetRate * improvementRate * effortMultiplier;\n    // Cap annual savings at 92% of the total baseline to guarantee conservative modeled overhead\n    const annualSavings = Math.min(parsedCost * 0.92, Math.max(0, rawSavings));\n\n    // Calculate Sovereign Platform Deployment Investment\n    // Modeled conservatively based on organization scale and transaction volume complexity\n    const baseScaleCost =\n      formData.companySize === \"10000+\"\n        ? 145000\n        : formData.companySize === \"1000-10000\"\n        ? 65000\n        : formData.companySize === \"100-1000\"\n        ? 28000\n        : 12000;\n\n    const variableComplexityCost = Math.min(180000, parsedCost * 0.04);\n    const estimatedInvestment = Math.round(baseScaleCost + variableComplexityCost);\n\n    // ROI Indicators\n    const netFirstYearSavings = Math.max(0, annualSavings - estimatedInvestment);\n    const roiPercentage = estimatedInvestment > 0 ? Math.round((annualSavings / estimatedInvestment) * 100) : 0;\n    \n    const monthlySavings = annualSavings / 12;\n    const paybackHorizonMonths =\n      monthlySavings > 0\n        ? Math.min(12, Math.max(1, Math.round((estimatedInvestment / monthlySavings) * 10) / 10))\n        : 12;\n\n    // Hours Saved Calculation (Optional metric if handling time exists)\n    const annualHoursSpent = (parsedVolume * parsedHandlingTime) / 60;\n    const hoursReclaimed = Math.round(annualHoursSpent * targetRate * improvementRate);\n\n    // Projected 3-Year Accumulation\n    const year2Savings = annualSavings * 1.05; // 5% efficiency ramp-up\n    const year3Savings = annualSavings * 1.10; // 10% efficiency ramp-up\n    const cumulativeThreeYearSavings = annualSavings + year2Savings + year3Savings - estimatedInvestment;\n\n    return {\n      annualSavings,\n      estimatedInvestment,\n      netFirstYearSavings,\n      roiPercentage,\n      paybackHorizonMonths,\n      hoursReclaimed,\n      annualHoursSpent,\n      cumulativeThreeYearSavings,\n      year2Savings,\n      year3Savings,\n    };\n  }, [formData, errors]);\n\n  // Handle Simulation Reveal\n  const triggerSimulation = () => {\n    if (Object.keys(errors).length > 0) return;\n    setIsSimulating(true);\n    setTimeout(() => {\n      setIsSimulating(false);\n      setShowReportModal(true);\n    }, 900);\n  };\n\n  return (\n    <ToolPageShell>\n      {/* Page Header */}\n      <div className=\"border-b border-white/5 pb-8 mb-10 flex flex-col lg:flex-row lg:items-end justify-between gap-6 animate-fadeIn\">\n        <div className=\"space-y-3 max-w-4xl\">\n          <span className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-[#009DFF] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest block\">\n            Operational Blueprinting\n          </span>\n          <h1 className=\"text-3xl lg:text-5xl font-extrabold text-white tracking-tight leading-none\">\n            Sovereign Enclave <span className=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-white via-white to-[#009DFF] bg-clip-text text-transparent\">ROI Calculator</span>\n          </h1>\n          <p className=\"text-white/60 text-xs lg:text-sm font-light max-w-2xl leading-relaxed\">\n            Perform enterprise-grade efficiency modeling. Graph the financial velocity, reclaimed bandwidth, and capital returns of private, watchdog-orchestrated AI nodes.\n          </p>\n        </div>\n\n        <div className=\"p-4 px-6 rounded-xl bg-white/[0.01] border border-white/5 flex flex-col items-start min-w-[210px] shrink-0\">\n          <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono text-white/40 uppercase tracking-widest\">Illustrative System Class</span>\n          <span className=\"text-xl font-bold text-[#00FF9D] mt-1 font-mono tracking-tight\">CLASS-IV ENCLAVE</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      {/* Main Dual-Pane Layout */}\n      <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8 items-start\">\n        \n        {/* LEFT COLUMN: The Input Panel */}\n        <div className=\"lg:col-span-5 space-y-6\">\n          <div className=\"p-6 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 bg-[#030305]/95 backdrop-blur-sm space-y-6 relative overflow-hidden\">\n            {/* Top accent bar */}\n            <div className=\"absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-[1px] bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-[#009DFF]/30 to-transparent pointer-events-none\" />\n            \n            <div className=\"flex items-center justify-between border-b border-white/5 pb-4\">\n              <h2 className=\"text-xs font-bold text-white uppercase tracking-wider font-mono flex items-center gap-2\">\n                <span className=\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-[#009DFF] animate-pulse\" />\n                MODEL PARAMETERS\n              </h2>\n              <span className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-white/40\">SECURE LOCAL BUFFER</span>\n            </div>\n\n            {/* Form Section 1: Firmographics */}\n            <div className=\"space-y-4\">\n              <h3 className=\"text-[10px] font-mono font-bold text-[#009DFF] uppercase tracking-wider\">\n                1. Firmographics & Domain\n              </h3>\n\n              {/* Industry Dropdown */}\n              <div className=\"space-y-1.5\">\n                <label className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-white/40 uppercase block\">Enterprise Industry</label>\n                <select\n                  value={formData.industry}\n                  onChange={(e) => handleInputChange(\"industry\", e.target.value)}\n                  className=\"w-full bg-[#080a10]/80 border border-white/5 rounded-lg px-3 py-2 text-xs text-white focus:outline-none focus:border-[#009DFF]/60 transition font-sans\"\n                >\n                  {SHARED_INDUSTRIES.map((ind) => (\n                    <option key={ind} value={ind} className=\"bg-[#030305] text-white\">\n                      {ind} Enterprise\n                    </option>\n                  ))}\n                </select>\n              </div>\n\n              {/* Company Size Segmented Control */}\n              <div className=\"space-y-1.5\">\n                <label className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-white/40 uppercase block\">Scale (FTE Count)</label>\n                <div className=\"grid grid-cols-4 gap-1 bg-[#080a10]/60 p-0.5 rounded-lg border border-white/5\">\n                  {SHARED_COMPANY_SIZES.map((size) => {\n                    const isActive = formData.companySize === size;\n                    return (\n                      <button\n                        key={size}\n                        type=\"button\"\n                        onClick={() => handleInputChange(\"companySize\", size)}\n                        className={`py-1.5 text-[10px] font-mono rounded-md transition ${\n                          isActive\n                            ? \"bg-[#009DFF]/15 text-[#009DFF] border border-[#009DFF]/30\"\n                            : \"text-white/40 hover:text-white/70 border border-transparent\"\n                        }`}\n                      >\n                        {size}\n                      </button>\n                    );\n                  })}\n                </div>\n              </div>\n\n              {/* Functional Domain */}\n              <div className=\"space-y-1.5\">\n                <label className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-white/40 uppercase block\">Functional Domain Target</label>\n                <div className=\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-2\">\n                  {functionalDomains.map((dom) => {\n                    const isActive = formData.functionalDomain === dom.id;\n                    return (\n                      <button\n                        key={dom.id}\n                        type=\"button\"\n                        onClick={() => handleInputChange(\"functionalDomain\", dom.id)}\n                        className={`flex items-center gap-2 p-2 rounded-lg border text-left transition ${\n                          isActive\n                            ? \"bg-[#009DFF]/5 border-[#009DFF]/30 text-white\"\n                            : \"bg-[#080a10]/40 border-white/5 text-white/50 hover:text-white/80\"\n                        }`}\n                      >\n                        <span className=\"text-xs\">{dom.icon}</span>\n                        <span className=\"text-[10px] font-medium truncate\">{dom.label}</span>\n                      </button>\n                    );\n                  })}\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n\n            {/* Form Section 2: Financials & Volume Inputs */}\n            <div className=\"space-y-4 pt-2 border-t border-white/5\">\n              <h3 className=\"text-[10px] font-mono font-bold text-[#009DFF] uppercase tracking-wider\">\n                2. Friction & Financial Baselines\n              </h3>\n\n              {/* Annual Cost Baseline */}\n              <div className=\"space-y-1.5 relative\">\n                <div className=\"flex justify-between items-baseline\">\n                  <label className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-white/40 uppercase block\">Annual Cost Baseline (USD)</label>\n                  {errors.annualCostBaseline && (\n                    <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono text-red-500 font-bold\">{errors.annualCostBaseline}</span>\n                  )}\n                </div>\n                <div className=\"relative\">\n                  <span className=\"absolute left-3 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 text-xs font-mono text-white/30\">$</span>\n                  <input\n                    type=\"text\"\n                    inputMode=\"numeric\"\n                    value={formData.annualCostBaseline}\n                    onChange={(e) => handleInputChange(\"annualCostBaseline\", e.target.value)}\n                    placeholder=\"e.g. 500000\"\n                    className={`w-full bg-[#080a10]/80 border ${\n                      errors.annualCostBaseline ? \"border-red-500/50\" : \"border-white/5\"\n                    } rounded-lg pl-7 pr-3 py-2 text-xs font-mono text-white focus:outline-none focus:border-[#009DFF]/60 transition`}\n                  />\n                </div>\n                <p className=\"text-[9px] text-white/30 font-light leading-snug\">\n                  Current fully loaded internal cost of manual processes in this scope.\n                </p>\n              </div>\n\n              {/* Process Volume & Average Handling Time Grid */}\n              <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n                {/* Process Volume */}\n                <div className=\"space-y-1.5\">\n                  <div className=\"flex justify-between items-baseline\">\n                    <label className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-white/40 uppercase block\">Annual Volume</label>\n                    {errors.processVolume && (\n                      <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono text-red-500 font-bold\">{errors.processVolume}</span>\n                    )}\n                  </div>\n                  <input\n                    type=\"text\"\n                    inputMode=\"numeric\"\n                    value={formData.processVolume}\n                    onChange={(e) => handleInputChange(\"processVolume\", e.target.value)}\n                    placeholder=\"e.g. 100000\"\n                    className={`w-full bg-[#080a10]/80 border ${\n                      errors.processVolume ? \"border-red-500/50\" : \"border-white/5\"\n                    } rounded-lg px-3 py-2 text-xs font-mono text-white focus:outline-none focus:border-[#009DFF]/60 transition`}\n                  />\n                  <p className=\"text-[9px] text-white/30 font-light leading-snug\">\n                    Tasks or cases processed per year.\n                  </p>\n                </div>\n\n                {/* Avg Handling Time (Optional) */}\n                <div className=\"space-y-1.5\">\n                  <div className=\"flex justify-between items-baseline\">\n                    <label className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-white/40 uppercase block\">Handling Time (Mins) <span className=\"text-[8px] opacity-60\">(Opt)</span></label>\n                    {errors.avgHandlingTime && (\n                      <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono text-red-500 font-bold\">{errors.avgHandlingTime}</span>\n                    )}\n                  </div>\n                  <input\n                    type=\"text\"\n                    inputMode=\"numeric\"\n                    value={formData.avgHandlingTime}\n                    onChange={(e) => handleInputChange(\"avgHandlingTime\", e.target.value)}\n                    placeholder=\"e.g. 15 (Optional)\"\n                    className={`w-full bg-[#080a10]/80 border ${\n                      errors.avgHandlingTime ? \"border-red-500/50\" : \"border-white/5\"\n                    } rounded-lg px-3 py-2 text-xs font-mono text-white focus:outline-none focus:border-[#009DFF]/60 transition`}\n                  />\n                  <p className=\"text-[9px] text-white/30 font-light leading-snug\">\n                    Minutes per task baseline.\n                  </p>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n\n            {/* Form Section 3: Sovereign Automation Goals */}\n            <div className=\"space-y-4 pt-2 border-t border-white/5\">\n              <h3 className=\"text-[10px] font-mono font-bold text-[#009DFF] uppercase tracking-wider\">\n                3. Automation target & Strategy\n              </h3>\n\n              {/* Automation Target Slider */}\n              <div className=\"space-y-2\">\n                <div className=\"flex justify-between items-baseline text-xs font-mono\">\n                  <span className=\"text-[10px] text-white/40 uppercase\">Automation Reach Target</span>\n                  <span className=\"text-[#00FF9D] font-bold\">{formData.automationTarget}%</span>\n                </div>\n                <input\n                  type=\"range\"\n                  min=\"10\"\n                  max=\"100\"\n                  step=\"5\"\n                  value={formData.automationTarget}\n                  onChange={(e) => handleInputChange(\"automationTarget\", parseInt(e.target.value))}\n                  className=\"w-full h-1 bg-white/5 rounded-lg appearance-none cursor-pointer accent-[#009DFF]\"\n                />\n                <div className=\"flex justify-between text-[8px] text-white/30 font-mono\">\n                  <span>10% (CRITICAL FLOWS)</span>\n                  <span>100% (FULL HANDS-OFF)</span>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n\n              {/* Current Manual Effort Level Segmented Control */}\n              <div className=\"space-y-1.5\">\n                <label className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-white/40 uppercase block\">Current Human Friction Level</label>\n                <div className=\"grid grid-cols-3 gap-1 bg-[#080a10]/60 p-0.5 rounded-lg border border-white/5\">\n                  {([\"Low\", \"Medium\", \"High\"] as const).map((lvl) => {\n                    const isActive = formData.currentManualEffort === lvl;\n                    return (\n                      <button\n                        key={lvl}\n                        type=\"button\"\n                        onClick={() => handleInputChange(\"currentManualEffort\", lvl)}\n                        className={`py-1 text-[10px] font-mono rounded-md transition ${\n                          isActive\n                            ? \"bg-[#009DFF]/15 text-[#009DFF] border border-[#009DFF]/30\"\n                            : \"text-white/40 hover:text-white/70 border border-transparent\"\n                        }`}\n                      >\n                        {lvl}\n                      </button>\n                    );\n                  })}\n                </div>\n                <p className=\"text-[9px] text-white/30 font-light leading-snug\">\n                  High friction processes represent maximum potential efficiency gains under sovereign watchdog triggers.\n                </p>\n              </div>\n\n              {/* Expected Productivity Improvement Slider */}\n              <div className=\"space-y-2\">\n                <div className=\"flex justify-between items-baseline text-xs font-mono\">\n                  <span className=\"text-[10px] text-white/40 uppercase\">Productivity Gain Intensity</span>\n                  <span className=\"text-[#009DFF] font-bold\">{formData.expectedProductivityImprovement}%</span>\n                </div>\n                <input\n                  type=\"range\"\n                  min=\"10\"\n                  max=\"90\"\n                  step=\"5\"\n                  value={formData.expectedProductivityImprovement}\n                  onChange={(e) => handleInputChange(\"expectedProductivityImprovement\", parseInt(e.target.value))}\n                  className=\"w-full h-1 bg-white/5 rounded-lg appearance-none cursor-pointer accent-[#009DFF]\"\n                />\n                <div className=\"flex justify-between text-[8px] text-white/30 font-mono\">\n                  <span>10% (ASSISTIVE COPILOT)</span>\n                  <span>90% (AUTONOMOUS SWARM)</span>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n\n              {/* Implementation Horizon Segmented Control */}\n              <div className=\"space-y-1.5\">\n                <label className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-white/40 uppercase block\">Target Deployment Horizon</label>\n                <div className=\"grid grid-cols-3 gap-1 bg-[#080a10]/60 p-0.5 rounded-lg border border-white/5\">\n                  {([\"3 Months\", \"6 Months\", \"12 Months\"] as const).map((hz) => {\n                    const isActive = formData.implementationHorizon === hz;\n                    return (\n                      <button\n                        key={hz}\n                        type=\"button\"\n                        onClick={() => handleInputChange(\"implementationHorizon\", hz)}\n                        className={`py-1 text-[10px] font-mono rounded-md transition ${\n                          isActive\n                            ? \"bg-[#009DFF]/15 text-[#009DFF] border border-[#009DFF]/30\"\n                            : \"text-white/40 hover:text-white/70 border border-transparent\"\n                        }`}\n                      >\n                        {hz}\n                      </button>\n                    );\n                  })}\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n\n            {/* Simulate Button */}\n            <div className=\"pt-4\">\n              <button\n                type=\"button\"\n                onClick={triggerSimulation}\n                disabled={Object.keys(errors).length > 0}\n                className={`w-full h-11 rounded-xl text-xs font-bold text-black bg-[#009DFF] hover:bg-[#009DFF]/90 transition uppercase tracking-wider flex items-center justify-center gap-2 group/btn shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(0,157,255,0.2)] ${\n                  Object.keys(errors).length > 0 ? \"opacity-50 cursor-not-allowed\" : \"\"\n                }`}\n              >\n                {isSimulating ? (\n                  <>\n                    <svg className=\"animate-spin h-4 w-4 text-black\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\">\n                      <circle className=\"opacity-25\" cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\" stroke=\"currentColor\" strokeWidth=\"4\" />\n                      <path className=\"opacity-75\" fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M4 12a8 8 0 018-8V0C5.373 0 0 5.373 0 12h4z\" />\n                    </svg>\n                    <span>COMPILING SIMULATION DIRECTIVES...</span>\n                  </>\n                ) : (\n                  <>\n                    <span>COMPILE SOVEREIGN REPORT</span>\n                    <svg className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5 group-hover/btn:translate-x-0.5 transition-transform\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\">\n                      <path strokeLinecap=\"round\" strokeLinejoin=\"round\" strokeWidth={2.5} d=\"M14 5l7 7m0 0l-7 7m7-7H3\" />\n                    </svg>\n                  </>\n                )}\n              </button>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n\n          {/* Compliance Sandbox Notice */}\n          <ToolPreviewNotice />\n        </div>\n\n        {/* RIGHT COLUMN: The Interactive Live Dashboard Preview */}\n        <div className=\"lg:col-span-7 space-y-6\">\n          <div className=\"p-6 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 bg-[#030305]/95 backdrop-blur-sm space-y-6 relative overflow-hidden\">\n            {/* Top scanning animation bar */}\n            <div className=\"absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-[1px] bg-[#00FF9D]/30 pointer-events-none\" />\n            \n            {/* Live telemetry status */}\n            <div className=\"flex items-center justify-between border-b border-white/5 pb-4\">\n              <div className=\"flex items-center gap-2\">\n                <span className=\"relative flex h-2 w-2\">\n                  <span className=\"animate-ping absolute inline-flex h-full w-full rounded-full bg-[#00FF9D] opacity-75\" />\n                  <span className=\"relative inline-flex rounded-full h-2 w-2 bg-[#00FF9D]\" />\n                </span>\n                <span className=\"text-xs font-bold text-white uppercase tracking-wider font-mono\">\n                  LIVE MODELLED PROJECTION\n                </span>\n              </div>\n              <span className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-[#00FF9D] bg-[#00FF9D]/10 border border-[#00FF9D]/20 px-2 py-0.5 rounded uppercase font-bold tracking-widest\">\n                RECALCULATING LIVE\n              </span>\n            </div>\n\n            {calculatedModel ? (\n              <div className=\"space-y-6 animate-fadeIn\">\n                {/* 1. Bento Grid KPIs */}\n                <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n                  {/* KPI Card 1: Reclaimed Capital */}\n                  <div className=\"p-5 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.01] hover:border-white/10 transition relative group\">\n                    <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono text-white/40 uppercase tracking-widest block\">\n                      NET FIRST-YEAR CAPITAL RECLAIMED\n                    </span>\n                    <span className=\"text-3xl font-extrabold font-mono text-[#00FF9D] mt-2 block tracking-tight\">\n                      ${calculatedModel.netFirstYearSavings.toLocaleString()}\n                    </span>\n                    <p className=\"text-[9px] text-white/30 font-light mt-1.5 leading-tight\">\n                      Annual gross savings of ${Math.round(calculatedModel.annualSavings).toLocaleString()} minus recommended sovereign VPC compute allocations.\n                    </p>\n                  </div>\n\n                  {/* KPI Card 2: Year 1 Return (ROI) */}\n                  <div className=\"p-5 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.01] hover:border-white/10 transition relative group\">\n                    <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono text-white/40 uppercase tracking-widest block\">\n                      ESTIMATED FIRST-YEAR RETURN\n                    </span>\n                    <span className=\"text-3xl font-extrabold font-mono text-[#009DFF] mt-2 block tracking-tight\">\n                      +{calculatedModel.roiPercentage}% ROI\n                    </span>\n                    <p className=\"text-[9px] text-white/30 font-light mt-1.5 leading-tight\">\n                      Sovereign enclaves deliver high ROI due to elimination of legacy SaaS subscriptions and API pipeline leakages.\n                    </p>\n                  </div>\n\n                  {/* KPI Card 3: Payback Milestone */}\n                  <div className=\"p-5 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.01] hover:border-white/10 transition relative group\">\n                    <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono text-white/40 uppercase tracking-widest block\">\n                      INVESTMENT RECOVERY HORIZON\n                    </span>\n                    <span className=\"text-2xl font-bold font-mono text-white mt-2 block tracking-tight\">\n                      {calculatedModel.paybackHorizonMonths} Months\n                    </span>\n                    <p className=\"text-[9px] text-white/30 font-light mt-1.5 leading-tight\">\n                      Complete amortization of single-tenant VPC setup and watchdogs based on internal labor metrics.\n                    </p>\n                  </div>\n\n                  {/* KPI Card 4: Hours Reclaimed */}\n                  <div className=\"p-5 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.01] hover:border-white/10 transition relative group\">\n                    <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono text-white/40 uppercase tracking-widest block\">\n                      RECLAIMED OPERATIONAL CAPACITY\n                    </span>\n                    {formData.avgHandlingTime ? (\n                      <span className=\"text-2xl font-bold font-mono text-white mt-2 block tracking-tight\">\n                        {calculatedModel.hoursReclaimed.toLocaleString()} Hrs/Yr\n                      </span>\n                    ) : (\n                      <span className=\"text-xs font-mono text-white/30 mt-3 block italic leading-snug\">\n                        Time savings require Average Handling Time input\n                      </span>\n                    )}\n                    <p className=\"text-[9px] text-white/30 font-light mt-1.5 leading-tight\">\n                      Enterprise capacity re-allocated back to strategic and advisory initiatives natively.\n                    </p>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n\n                {/* 2. Dynamic Agent Workflow Diagram */}\n                <div className=\"p-5 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-[#06080e]/40 space-y-3\">\n                  <div className=\"flex justify-between items-baseline\">\n                    <span className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-white/40 uppercase tracking-wider block\">\n                      Sovereign Enclave Watchdog Flow\n                    </span>\n                    <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono text-[#009DFF] uppercase font-bold\">\n                      {formData.functionalDomain} Domain\n                    </span>\n                  </div>\n\n                  {/* Pure CSS/SVG Dynamic Architecture Map */}\n                  <div className=\"p-4 rounded-lg bg-black/60 border border-white/5 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-3 text-center md:text-left min-h-[100px] relative overflow-hidden\">\n                    <div className=\"absolute top-1/2 left-0 right-0 h-0.5 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#009DFF]/0 via-[#009DFF]/20 to-[#009DFF]/0 -translate-y-1/2 hidden md:block\" />\n                    \n                    {/* Step 1: Ingest */}\n                    <div className=\"relative z-10 p-2.5 px-3.5 rounded bg-white/[0.02] border border-white/5 w-full md:w-1/3\">\n                      <div className=\"text-[9px] font-mono text-[#009DFF] uppercase font-bold\">INGEST PERIMETER</div>\n                      <div className=\"text-[11px] font-bold text-white mt-0.5\">Secure Enclave Inlet</div>\n                      <div className=\"text-[9px] text-white/40 font-mono mt-1\">\n                        {formData.industry} Ingest\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n\n                    {/* Arrow / Connection */}\n                    <div className=\"text-[#009DFF] font-bold text-sm select-none animate-pulse rotate-90 md:rotate-0\">\n                      →\n                    </div>\n\n                    {/* Step 2: The Core Watchdog (Consensus Engine) */}\n                    <div className=\"relative z-10 p-2.5 px-3.5 rounded bg-[#009DFF]/5 border border-[#009DFF]/30 w-full md:w-1/3 shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(0,157,255,0.1)]\">\n                      <div className=\"text-[9px] font-mono text-[#00FF9D] uppercase font-bold\">CONSENSUS WATCHDOG</div>\n                      <div className=\"text-[11px] font-bold text-white mt-0.5\">Sovereign Validation</div>\n                      <div className=\"text-[9px] text-white/40 font-mono mt-1\">\n                        {formData.functionalDomain} Agents\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n\n                    {/* Arrow / Connection */}\n                    <div className=\"text-[#009DFF] font-bold text-sm select-none animate-pulse rotate-90 md:rotate-0\">\n                      →\n                    </div>\n\n                    {/* Step 3: Outflow */}\n                    <div className=\"relative z-10 p-2.5 px-3.5 rounded bg-white/[0.02] border border-white/5 w-full md:w-1/3\">\n                      <div className=\"text-[9px] font-mono text-white/40 uppercase font-bold\">AIR-GAPPED OUTFLOW</div>\n                      <div className=\"text-[11px] font-bold text-white mt-0.5\">0% Storage Commit</div>\n                      <div className=\"text-[9px] text-[#00FF9D] font-mono mt-1\">No Trace Retained</div>\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n\n                {/* 3. Implementation Milestone Timeline */}\n                <div className=\"p-5 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.01] space-y-4\">\n                  <div className=\"flex justify-between items-baseline\">\n                    <span className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-white/40 uppercase tracking-wider block\">\n                      DEPLOYMENT ARCHITECTURE ROADMAP\n                    </span>\n                    <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono text-[#00FF9D] uppercase font-bold\">\n                      Horizon: {formData.implementationHorizon}\n                    </span>\n                  </div>\n\n                  {/* Dynamic Timeline Component */}\n                  <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 pt-2\">\n                    {formData.implementationHorizon === \"3 Months\" ? (\n                      <>\n                        <div className=\"p-3.5 rounded-lg border border-white/5 bg-[#030305]/50 relative\">\n                          <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono text-[#009DFF] uppercase font-bold block\">MONTH 1</span>\n                          <span className=\"text-xs font-bold text-white mt-1 block\">VPC Node Provisioning</span>\n                          <p className=\"text-[10px] text-white/40 font-light mt-1\">Provision single-tenant private subnets inside secure regional clouds.</p>\n                        </div>\n                        <div className=\"p-3.5 rounded-lg border border-white/5 bg-[#030305]/50 relative\">\n                          <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono text-[#009DFF] uppercase font-bold block\">MONTH 2</span>\n                          <span className=\"text-xs font-bold text-white mt-1 block\">Fine-Tuning & Ingest</span>\n                          <p className=\"text-[10px] text-white/40 font-light mt-1\">Construct secure vector indices and ingest baseline schemas locally.</p>\n                        </div>\n                        <div className=\"p-3.5 rounded-lg border border-[#00FF9D]/20 bg-[#00FF9D]/5 relative\">\n                          <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono text-[#00FF9D] uppercase font-bold block\">MONTH 3</span>\n                          <span className=\"text-xs font-bold text-white mt-1 block\">Live Watchdog Hand-off</span>\n                          <p className=\"text-[10px] text-white/40 font-light mt-1\">Activate strict consensus validators. Transition operational custody.</p>\n                        </div>\n                      </>\n                    ) : formData.implementationHorizon === \"6 Months\" ? (\n                      <>\n                        <div className=\"p-3.5 rounded-lg border border-white/5 bg-[#030305]/50 relative\">\n                          <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono text-[#009DFF] uppercase font-bold block\">MONTHS 1-2</span>\n                          <span className=\"text-xs font-bold text-white mt-1 block\">Sovereign Architecture Design</span>\n                          <p className=\"text-[10px] text-white/40 font-light mt-1\">Establish secure compliance baselines and private single-tenant subnets.</p>\n                        </div>\n                        <div className=\"p-3.5 rounded-lg border border-white/5 bg-[#030305]/50 relative\">\n                          <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono text-[#009DFF] uppercase font-bold block\">MONTHS 3-4</span>\n                          <span className=\"text-xs font-bold text-white mt-1 block\">Workflow Integration & DAGs</span>\n                          <p className=\"text-[10px] text-white/40 font-light mt-1\">Build autonomous decision DAGs and calibrate local guardrail systems.</p>\n                        </div>\n                        <div className=\"p-3.5 rounded-lg border border-[#00FF9D]/20 bg-[#00FF9D]/5 relative\">\n                          <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono text-[#00FF9D] uppercase font-bold block\">MONTHS 5-6</span>\n                          <span className=\"text-xs font-bold text-white mt-1 block\">Consensus Audit & Live Scale</span>\n                          <p className=\"text-[10px] text-white/40 font-light mt-1\">Simulate network load, verify zero-leak compliance, and open keys to local IT.</p>\n                        </div>\n                      </>\n                    ) : (\n                      <>\n                        <div className=\"p-3.5 rounded-lg border border-white/5 bg-[#030305]/50 relative\">\n                          <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono text-[#009DFF] uppercase font-bold block\">MONTHS 1-3</span>\n                          <span className=\"text-xs font-bold text-white mt-1 block\">Global VPC Engineering</span>\n                          <p className=\"text-[10px] text-white/40 font-light mt-1\">Orchestrate highly resilient, multi-region single-tenant sovereign VPC clusters.</p>\n                        </div>\n                        <div className=\"p-3.5 rounded-lg border border-white/5 bg-[#030305]/50 relative\">\n                          <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono text-[#009DFF] uppercase font-bold block\">MONTHS 4-7</span>\n                          <span className=\"text-xs font-bold text-white mt-1 block\">Vector Fine-Tuning & Pilots</span>\n                          <p className=\"text-[10px] text-white/40 font-light mt-1\">Tune localized enclaves against proprietary schemas with 0 remote logs.</p>\n                        </div>\n                        <div className=\"p-3.5 rounded-lg border border-[#00FF9D]/20 bg-[#00FF9D]/5 relative\">\n                          <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono text-[#00FF9D] uppercase font-bold block\">MONTHS 8-12</span>\n                          <span className=\"text-xs font-bold text-white mt-1 block\">Watchdog Consensus Launch</span>\n                          <p className=\"text-[10px] text-white/40 font-light mt-1\">Launch comprehensive enterprise agent factories with localized telemetry gates.</p>\n                        </div>\n                      </>\n                    )}\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n\n                {/* 4. Model Footnote Disclaimer */}\n                <div className=\"flex justify-between items-center text-[10px] text-white/30 font-mono border-t border-white/5 pt-4\">\n                  <span>MODEL VERSION: v2.26.1</span>\n                  <span>* ILLUSTRATIVE PROJECTION ONLY. NO ROI GUARANTEED.</span>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            ) : (\n              <div className=\"p-12 text-center rounded-xl border border-dashed border-white/10 bg-white/[0.01] flex flex-col items-center justify-center space-y-3\">\n                <svg className=\"w-8 h-8 text-red-500/50\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\">\n                  <path strokeLinecap=\"round\" strokeLinejoin=\"round\" strokeWidth={1.5} d=\"M12 9v2m0 4h.01m-6.938 4h13.856c1.54 0 2.502-1.667 1.732-3L13.732 4c-.77-1.333-2.694-1.333-3.464 0L3.34 16c-.77 1.333.192 3 1.732 3z\" />\n                </svg>\n                <span className=\"text-xs text-white/60 font-mono font-bold uppercase\">MODEL ERROR INHIBIT</span>\n                <p className=\"text-[11px] text-white/40 font-light max-w-sm\">\n                  Please resolve the red input errors inside the left parameter panel to recalculate the dynamic sovereign projections.\n                </p>\n              </div>\n            )}\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      {/* Static Footer Technical CTA */}\n      <ToolCTA />\n\n      {/* EXECUTIVE SIMULATION REPORT MODAL */}\n      <AnimatePresence>\n        {showReportModal && calculatedModel && (\n          <div className=\"fixed inset-0 z-50 flex items-center justify-center p-4 bg-[#020204]/90 backdrop-blur-md overflow-y-auto\">\n            <motion.div\n              initial={{ opacity: 0, scale: 0.95, y: 15 }}\n              animate={{ opacity: 1, scale: 1, y: 0 }}\n              exit={{ opacity: 0, scale: 0.95, y: 15 }}\n              transition={{ duration: 0.4, ease: [0.16, 1, 0.3, 1] }}\n              className=\"relative w-full max-w-4xl rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-[#030305] p-6 md:p-10 shadow-3xl text-white my-8 overflow-hidden\"\n            >\n              {/* Laser Accent line */}\n              <div className=\"absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-[2px] bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-[#009DFF] to-[#00FF9D]\" />\n              \n              {/* Decorative side blurs */}\n              <div className=\"absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-[500px] h-[500px] bg-[#009DFF]/5 blur-3xl pointer-events-none rounded-full\" />\n\n              {/* Close Button */}\n              <button\n                type=\"button\"\n                onClick={() => setShowReportModal(false)}\n                className=\"absolute top-6 right-6 p-2 rounded-lg border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.02] hover:bg-white/[0.08] transition text-white/60 hover:text-white\"\n              >\n                <svg className=\"w-4 h-4\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\">\n                  <path strokeLinecap=\"round\" strokeLinejoin=\"round\" strokeWidth={2} d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\" />\n                </svg>\n              </button>\n\n              {/* Modal Content */}\n              <div className=\"space-y-8 relative z-10\">\n                \n                {/* Header */}\n                <div className=\"space-y-2 border-b border-white/5 pb-6\">\n                  <div className=\"flex items-center gap-3\">\n                    <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono text-[#00FF9D] border border-[#00FF9D]/30 bg-[#00FF9D]/10 px-2 py-0.5 rounded font-bold uppercase tracking-wider\">\n                      COMPILED BLUEPRINT\n                    </span>\n                    <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono text-white/40\">GFF_SOVEREIGN_ENGINE_v2.26</span>\n                  </div>\n                  <h2 className=\"text-xl md:text-3xl font-extrabold tracking-tight\">\n                    Sovereign Enclave Specification Sheet\n                  </h2>\n                  <p className=\"text-xs text-white/50 font-light max-w-2xl leading-relaxed\">\n                    Modeled for <span className=\"text-white font-bold\">{formData.industry}</span>, scaling across <span className=\"text-white font-bold\">{formData.companySize} FTEs</span> inside the <span className=\"text-white font-bold\">{formData.functionalDomain}</span> domain.\n                  </p>\n                </div>\n\n                {/* Grid Details */}\n                <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6\">\n                  <div className=\"p-4 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-[#080a10]/50\">\n                    <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono text-white/40 uppercase tracking-wider block\">RECOMMENDED VPC INVESTMENT</span>\n                    <span className=\"text-2xl font-extrabold font-mono text-white mt-1 block\">\n                      ${calculatedModel.estimatedInvestment.toLocaleString()}\n                    </span>\n                    <p className=\"text-[10px] text-white/40 font-light mt-1.5 leading-snug\">\n                      Modeled for high availability, zero log retention compute nodes, and localized guardrail structures.\n                    </p>\n                  </div>\n\n                  <div className=\"p-4 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-[#080a10]/50\">\n                    <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono text-white/40 uppercase tracking-wider block\">PROJECTED YEAR 1 SAVINGS</span>\n                    <span className=\"text-2xl font-extrabold font-mono text-[#00FF9D] mt-1 block\">\n                      ${Math.round(calculatedModel.annualSavings).toLocaleString()}\n                    </span>\n                    <p className=\"text-[10px] text-white/40 font-light mt-1.5 leading-snug\">\n                      Calculated at a target reach of {formData.automationTarget}% with localized consensus watchdog execution.\n                    </p>\n                  </div>\n\n                  <div className=\"p-4 rounded-xl border border-[#009DFF]/20 bg-[#009DFF]/5\">\n                    <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono text-[#009DFF] uppercase tracking-wider font-bold block\">ESTIMATED FIRST-YEAR RETURN</span>\n                    <span className=\"text-2xl font-extrabold font-mono text-[#009DFF] mt-1 block\">\n                      {calculatedModel.roiPercentage}% ROI\n                    </span>\n                    <p className=\"text-[10px] text-white/40 font-light mt-1.5 leading-snug\">\n                      Investment payback anticipated in {calculatedModel.paybackHorizonMonths} months of production watchdog runtime.\n                    </p>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n\n                {/* 3-Year Cumulative Projections Breakdown Table/Graph */}\n                <div className=\"p-5 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-[#06080e]/40 space-y-4\">\n                  <h3 className=\"text-xs font-bold font-mono text-white uppercase tracking-wider\">\n                    Cumulative Sovereign Efficiency Forecast\n                  </h3>\n                  \n                  <div className=\"space-y-3.5\">\n                    {/* Year 1 */}\n                    <div className=\"space-y-1\">\n                      <div className=\"flex justify-between text-xs font-mono\">\n                        <span className=\"text-white/50\">Year 1 Net Savings (After Setup Compute Allocation)</span>\n                        <span className=\"text-[#00FF9D] font-bold\">${Math.round(calculatedModel.netFirstYearSavings).toLocaleString()}</span>\n                      </div>\n                      <div className=\"w-full h-2 bg-white/5 rounded-full overflow-hidden\">\n                        <div className=\"h-full bg-gradient-to-r from-[#009DFF] to-[#00FF9D]\" style={{ width: \"33%\" }} />\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n\n                    {/* Year 2 */}\n                    <div className=\"space-y-1\">\n                      <div className=\"flex justify-between text-xs font-mono\">\n                        <span className=\"text-white/50\">Year 2 Net Savings (5% Model Optimization Ramp)</span>\n                        <span className=\"text-[#00FF9D] font-bold\">${Math.round(calculatedModel.year2Savings).toLocaleString()}</span>\n                      </div>\n                      <div className=\"w-full h-2 bg-white/5 rounded-full overflow-hidden\">\n                        <div className=\"h-full bg-gradient-to-r from-[#009DFF] to-[#00FF9D]\" style={{ width: \"66%\" }} />\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n\n                    {/* Year 3 */}\n                    <div className=\"space-y-1\">\n                      <div className=\"flex justify-between text-xs font-mono\">\n                        <span className=\"text-white/50\">Year 3 Net Savings (10% Swarm Optimization Ramp)</span>\n                        <span className=\"text-[#00FF9D] font-bold\">${Math.round(calculatedModel.year3Savings).toLocaleString()}</span>\n                      </div>\n                      <div className=\"w-full h-2 bg-white/5 rounded-full overflow-hidden\">\n                        <div className=\"h-full bg-gradient-to-r from-[#009DFF] to-[#00FF9D]\" style={{ width: \"100%\" }} />\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n\n                  <div className=\"bg-black/40 p-3.5 rounded-lg border border-white/5 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-4 text-center md:text-left\">\n                    <div>\n                      <span className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-white/40 uppercase block\">CUMULATIVE 3-YEAR NET ADVANTAGE</span>\n                      <span className=\"text-xl font-bold font-mono text-[#00FF9D] mt-0.5 block\">\n                        ${Math.round(calculatedModel.cumulativeThreeYearSavings).toLocaleString()} Reclaimed\n                      </span>\n                    </div>\n                    <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono text-white/30 italic\">\n                      Zero-retention local compute architectures significantly compress traditional cloud subscription premiums.\n                    </span>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n\n                {/* Narrative Summary paragraph */}\n                <div className=\"p-5 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-[#030305]/80 space-y-2\">\n                  <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono text-white/40 uppercase tracking-widest block font-bold\">EXECUTIVE SUMMARY STATEMENT</span>\n                  <p className=\"text-xs text-white/70 leading-relaxed font-light font-serif\">\n                    Deploying a secure, watchdog-orchestrated enclave inside a private <span className=\"text-white font-bold\">{formData.industry}</span> cloud segment yields a highly responsive, air-gapped system. By processing <span className=\"text-white font-bold\">{parseFloat(formData.processVolume).toLocaleString()} annual transactions</span> through consensus-based nodes, the <span className=\"text-white font-bold\">{formData.functionalDomain}</span> domain is projected to reduce active resource drag by <span className=\"text-[#009DFF] font-bold\">{formData.expectedProductivityImprovement}%</span>. This completely mitigates the regulatory compliance leakages of remote API layers while returning substantial operational throughput in under <span className=\"text-white font-bold\">{calculatedModel.paybackHorizonMonths} months</span>.\n                  </p>\n                </div>\n\n                {/* Footer and Call to action */}\n                <div className=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-6 border-t border-white/5 pt-6\">\n                  <p className=\"text-[10px] text-white/30 font-mono leading-snug max-w-md text-center sm:text-left\">\n                    * Projections are illustrative models only and do not constitute a contractually guaranteed performance level. Computed deterministically on secure local sandbox buffers.\n                  </p>\n\n                  <div className=\"flex items-center gap-3\">\n                    <button\n                      type=\"button\"\n                      onClick={() => setShowReportModal(false)}\n                      className=\"px-4 py-2.5 rounded-lg border border-white/10 hover:bg-white/5 text-xs text-white/80 font-mono uppercase transition\"\n                    >\n                      Close Report\n                    </button>\n                    <a\n                      href=\"/contact\"\n                      className=\"px-5 py-2.5 rounded-lg text-xs font-bold text-black bg-[#00FF9D] hover:bg-[#00FF9D]/90 transition uppercase tracking-wider inline-flex items-center gap-2 shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(0,255,157,0.2)]\"\n                    >\n                      <span>Secure Tech Sync</span>\n                      <svg className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\">\n                        <path strokeLinecap=\"round\" strokeLinejoin=\"round\" strokeWidth={2.5} d=\"M14 5l7 7m0 0l-7 7m7-7H3\" />\n                      </svg>\n                    </a>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </motion.div>\n          </div>\n        )}\n      </AnimatePresence>\n    </ToolPageShell>\n  );\n}\n"}}}
